org.dyn4j.collision.narrowphase

Class PairwiseTypedFallbackCondition

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.dyn4j.collision.narrowphase.AbstractFallbackCondition
      • org.dyn4j.collision.narrowphase.TypedFallbackCondition
        • org.dyn4j.collision.narrowphase.PairwiseTypedFallbackCondition
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<FallbackCondition>, FallbackCondition

    public class PairwiseTypedFallbackCondition
extends TypedFallbackCondition
implements FallbackCondition, java.lang.Comparable<FallbackCondition>
    Represents a TypedFallbackCondition that filters on a particular pair of types.

    If the pair Convex types match this pair, then the condition is met.

    Since:
    3.1.5
    Version:
    3.1.5
    Author:
    William Bittle
